data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 2-story four bedroom, three bath home situated on 1.24 acres.  Updated kitchen showcases granite counter tops and painted cabinets, and a beautiful custom wall coat tree has been added in the entryway.  There is also newer flooring throughout the home, and the roof was replaced in 2022.  The three car heated garage enters into the laundry room which includes a half bath. Underground sprinkler system will keep the yard looking fantastic. The location of the home on a cul-de-sac minimizes traffic.  This home has been very well maintained, and has great curb appeal.
